org.apache.giraph.yarn

类 YarnUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.giraph.yarn.YarnUtils

  • public class YarnUtils
extends Object
    Utilities that can only compile with versions of Hadoop that support YARN, so they live here instead of o.a.g.utils package.

    • 方法详细资料

      • addFsResourcesToMap

        public static void addFsResourcesToMap(Map<String,LocalResource> map,
                       GiraphConfiguration giraphConf,
                       ApplicationId appId)
                                throws IOException
        Populates the LocalResources list with the HDFS paths listed in the conf under GiraphConstants.GIRAPH_YARN_LIBJARS, and the GiraphConfiguration for this job. Also adds the Giraph default application jar as determined by GiraphYarnClient.GIRAPH_CLIENT_JAR constant.
        参数:
        map - the LocalResources list to populate.
        giraphConf - the configuration to use to select jars to include.
        appId - the ApplicationId, naming the the HDFS base dir for job jars.
        抛出:
        IOException

      • getLocalFiles

        public static Set<org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path> getLocalFiles(Set<String> fileNames)
        Utility function to locate local JAR files and other resources recursively in the dirs on the local CLASSPATH. Once all the files named in fileNames are found, we stop and return the results.
        参数:
        fileNames - the file name of the jars, without path information.
        返回:
        a set of Paths to the jar files requested in fileNames.

      • addFileToResourceMap

        public static void addFileToResourceMap(Map<String,LocalResource> localResources,
                        org.apache.hadoop.fs.FileSystem fs,
                        org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path target)
                                 throws IOException
        Boilerplate to add a file to the local resources..
        参数:
        localResources - the LocalResources map to populate.
        fs - handle to the HDFS file system.
        target - the file to send to the remote container.
        抛出:
        IOException

      • getFsCachePath

        public static org.apache.hadoop.fs.Path getFsCachePath(org.apache.hadoop.fs.FileSystem fs,
                                       ApplicationId appId)
        Get the base HDFS dir we will be storing our LocalResources in.
        参数:
        fs - the file system.
        appId - the ApplicationId under which our resources will be stored.
        返回:
        the path

      • addLocalClasspathToEnv

        public static void addLocalClasspathToEnv(Map<String,String> env,
                          GiraphConfiguration giraphConf)
        Popuate the environment string map to be added to the environment vars in a remote execution container. Adds the local classpath to pick up "yarn-site.xml" and "mapred-site.xml" stuff.
        参数:
        env - the map of env var values.
        giraphConf - the GiraphConfiguration to pull values from.

      • addGiraphConfToLocalResourceMap

        public static void addGiraphConfToLocalResourceMap(GiraphConfiguration giraphConf,
                                   ApplicationId appId,
                                   Map<String,LocalResource> localResourceMap)
                                            throws IOException
        Populate the LocalResources list with the GiraphConf XML file's HDFS path.
        参数:
        giraphConf - the GiraphConfifuration to export for worker tasks.
        appId - the ApplicationId for this YARN app.
        localResourceMap - the LocalResource map of files to export to tasks.
        抛出:
        IOException

      • exportGiraphConfiguration

        public static void exportGiraphConfiguration(GiraphConfiguration giraphConf,
                             ApplicationId appId)
                                      throws IOException
        Export our populated GiraphConfiguration as an XML file to be used by the ApplicationMaster's exec container, and register it with LocalResources.
        参数:
        giraphConf - the current Configuration object to be published.
        appId - the ApplicationId to stamp this app's base HDFS resources dir.
        抛出:
        IOException
